Listen, it's dangerous to think that way.

99
00:06:40,620 --> 00:06:42,100
Are you under his mind control?

100
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:45,700
Although Lord Qiansui
is not a good person either,

101
00:06:46,100 --> 00:06:47,980
