108
00:07:16,900 --> 00:07:17,660
Before that,

109
00:07:18,140 --> 00:07:19,700
I need you to do one last thing.

110
00:07:20,540 --> 00:07:23,020
(Indeed, Lord Qiansui is not a good guy.)

111
00:07:23,860 --> 00:07:24,380
Okay.

112
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:26,900
